notes.note:
Good afternoon, thank you for your previous email with the estimate for the required repairs on Laurie's Silverado. Unfortunately, wiring repairs are not covered under the customer's contract, however, the replacement of the water pump and starter motor is. Please be advised, the customer is responsible for any diagnostic fees and shop supplies, as well as a $100 deductible + tax. Additionally, our Mitchell Labour Guide allows for 2.7 hours labour for the water pump and starter motor replacement (1.0 hour for starter, 1.7 hour for water pump). I have increased the allowed labour time to 2.9 hours as a courtesy, since your dealer is a selling dealer and authorized repair facility. The payout is as follows:

Parts-$655.44
Labour-$377.00 (2.9 hours x $130/h)
Deductible-$100.00 + tax
Tax-$121.22
Authorization-APZ19NZ136

Total = $1053.66

Once the repair is complete, please send us a copy of the final invoice for payment.

Best regards, 

Matthew Puls
Claims Adjuster
